  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 400\u00042f (200\u00042c).",
    "cook the farfalle pasta according to the package instructions until al dente. drain and set aside.",
    "grill the pineapple, mango, red onion, and cilantro on a robata grill or in a grill pan until lightly charred.",
    "in a pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat. add the grilled pineapple, mango, and red onion, and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "add the cooked farfalle pasta, parmesan cheese, honey mixture, and soy sauce to the pan. toss to combine and heat through for 1-2 minutes.",
    "season with salt and pepper to taste. serve hot and garnish with additional cilantro if desired."
